                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 42,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Tartaglia_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Tartaglia",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Voice-Overs",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "About Skirk",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It's been years since I last saw my master. I should hope that next we meet, I'll at least be able to force her to use both hands to beat me...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold"
                      ],
                      "text": "Character Story",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Character Story 4",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Unlike what the rest of the world may think, Tartaglia was not born with his exceptional skills in battle.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "But he would never speak to anyone about that critical, fateful encounter of his...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "When he was 14, he fled his monotonous life at home with nothing but a shortsword and a bag of bread in hand.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "That 14-year-old boy got lost in the snowy forest.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Pursued by bears and wolf packs, he lost his footing and fell into a bottomless crack in the earth's surface.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "There, he witnessed the endless possibilities of another ancient world. There, he would meet a mysterious swordswoman...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Or perhaps one should say that this dark realm had sensed the burning ambition in this boy's heart.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "This darkness was something that the Harbinger Childe could never again delve into.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "In those three months, the swordswoman taught Tartaglia how to pass through the Abyss unhindered, and more importantly, nurtured the ability to stir up endless havoc from within Ajax's trouble-mongering nature.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "No one knew what happened within that darkness during those three months, nor would Ajax ever speak of this to anyone.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "When his worried mother and sisters finally found him in that forest, only 3 days had passed in this world.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Thus did Ajax's first adventure end, with his now-rusty shortsword in hand.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "This would mark the end of his youth and the beginning of his days as a warrior.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
